---
// src/components/SavedMoment.astro
// "All beliefs tended" confirmation toast — emotional payoff when the
// last endangered post is revived and the band empties.
//
// Hidden by default. Client script (endangeredClientScript) adds
// .saved-moment--visible when checkEmpty() finds no remaining cards.
// CSS animation handles the full cycle: fade-in → hold → fade-out.
//
// Also fires when a remote user revives the last post via SSE —
// the same dismissBand() path triggers it in both cases.
//
// Credits: Mike (napkin plan §3 — SavedMoment spec),
//          Tanya (UX spec — emotional payoff, "The record holds")
---

<div class="saved-moment" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
  All beliefs tended. The record holds.
</div>
